A '''letter of marque''' was a license under which a [[privateer]] conducted raids upon hostile entities on behalf of an authority. The [[Delphidian]] [[Sidon Ithano]] was granted one such letter, allowing him to operate along the [[Ootmian Pabol]], the [[Pabol Hutta]], the [[Shag Pabol]], and all the secular [[hyperspace]] [[Hyperspace route|routes]] of [[Hutt Space]], and to deliver the captured cargoes unto his [[Hutt]] patrons&mdash;of the [[Desilijic]], [[Ramesh]], [[Besadii]], [[Gnuda]], and [[Shell]] families&mdash;during the execution of official [[kajidic]] business.<ref name="Smuggler's Guide">''[[Star Wars: Smuggler's Guide]]''</ref>

Letters of marque distinguished privateers from other kinds of [[pirate]]s.<ref name="Smuggler's Guide" />

